      <article class="card">
        <h2>Welcome to ADMIFMS</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the Alkesh Dinesh Mody Institute for Financial and Management Studies (ADMIFMS), a distinguished department of the University of Mumbai committed to excellence in management and finance education. At ADMIFMS, we take immense pride in nurturing competent, ethical, and industry-ready professionals who are equipped to meet the evolving expectations of the corporate world and society at large.</p>
        <p>Over the years, the institute has earned recognition among the leading Government B-Schools in India through reputed national surveys conducted by Fortune India, India Today, The Week, and Business Today for the academic year 2024–25, particularly for delivering strong academic value and return on investment.</p>
        
        <h2>Institute Philosophy</h2>
        <p>At ADMIFMS, we believe that education extends beyond classrooms and textbooks. Our philosophy is rooted in creating a holistic and transformative learning environment that integrates academic rigor, industry relevance, ethical values, innovation, and social responsibility.</p>
        <p>Aligned with the vision of NEP 2020, the institute follows a progressive curriculum that emphasizes experiential learning, critical thinking, multidisciplinary exposure, and continuous skill enhancement. We are committed to fostering intellectual curiosity, leadership, entrepreneurship, and lifelong learning among our students.</p>
        <p>The institute also strongly promotes a culture of research and knowledge creation. Our faculty members actively contribute through research fellowships, consultancy assignments, funded projects, and socially impactful initiatives. A significant milestone in this direction was the successful completion of the ICSSR-sponsored Special Call Collaborative Empirical Research Project in partnership with Gujarat University and Ahmedabad University in March 2024.</p>
        
        <h2>Academic and student development focus</h2>
        <p>The institute continuously strives to bridge the gap between academia and industry through diverse student-centric initiatives and corporate engagement activities. Programmes such as the Summer Internship Award, Budget Prediction Competition, Career-pe-Charcha, Campus to Corporate Lecture Series, Corporate Mock Interviews, and ADM Memorial Lecture Series provide students with practical insights and professional exposure.</p>
        <p>To enhance employability and future readiness, the institute organizes regular up-skilling initiatives including Advanced MS-Excel Training Sessions, professional development workshops, and industry interaction programmes. The active participation of alumni through initiatives such as Coffee with Alumni further strengthens mentoring, networking, and career guidance opportunities for students.</p>
        <p>Our dedicated Placement Cell and strong industry partnerships have consistently contributed to successful summer and final placement outcomes across sectors. The institute’s efforts and contributions have also been recognized through prestigious honours including:

          <ol>
          <li>MCX Award 2025 for ‘Best Supporting Partner in Education, Awareness & Financial Literacy’</li>
          <li>‘Best Academic Partner’ recognition by ISTD (Mumbai Chapter)</li>
          <li>Skill Development Leadership Award 2025 by the World HRD Congress</li>
          </ol>
          </p>
          <p>Further, under the University Department Ranking Framework (UDRF) 2024–25, ADMIFMS secured First Rank in the category of “Best Institute in Management, Sub-Campus, Model College and Institutions” and also received First Rank as the “Best Academic Department for Administration.”
          </p>
        
        <h2>Message to Students and Parents</h2>
        <p>I encourage existing and future students of ADMIFMS  to make the most of the opportunities available at ADMIFMS. Participate actively in academic, co-curricular, and professional development activities, remain curious, and continuously strive for excellence. Your commitment, discipline, and willingness to learn will shape your future and help you emerge as confident professionals and responsible citizens.</p>
        <p>I assure you that the institute remains committed to providing a nurturing, intellectually stimulating, and value-based learning environment that supports the holistic growth and career aspirations of students.</p>
        <p>At ADMIFMS, we believe in building not only successful careers but also responsible leaders who can contribute meaningfully to organizations, communities, and society.</p>

        <p>I warmly welcome aspiring students, academic collaborators, alumni, and industry partners to become a part of the ADMIFMS journey of excellence, innovation, and growth. We look forward to building enduring relationships and creating new opportunities for learning, research, and professional success. </p>          
        <p><strong>Dr. Smita Shukla</strong></p>
        <p>Director & Professor, ADMIFMS</p>
      </article>
